{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"metadata": {"Header 1": "**\ud83e\udde0 The Big Lesson (Very Important)**"}, "page_content": "When \"nothing happens\" in a form:  \n### **Always check in this order:**  \n- Is the button disabled?\n- Does onPress fire?\n- Did validation fail?\n- Did parent receive payload?\n- Did API fire?\n- Did success callback execute?  \nForms fail in layers.\nDebug layer by layer.", "type": "Document"}}